Package: deepReveal
Title: A Framework for Sensitivity Analysis of Ecological Neural Networks
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Ulrike", "Hiltner", email = "ulrike.hiltner@usys.ethz.ch", role = c("aut", "cre"),
              comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-5663-7068"))
Description: Provides a suite of tools to conduct comprehensive sensitivity analyses on complex predictive models, 
    particularly neural networks used in ecological and environmental modeling. Includes functions for 
    permutation feature importance, analysis of model sensitivity to variations in feature values, 
    and assessment of performance across different feature sets.
